• <strong>刷新接口防护</strong>：<br>
<code v-pre>java       @PostMapping(&quot;/token/refresh&quot;)       public ResponseEntity&lt;JwtResponse&gt; refreshToken(@RequestParam String refreshToken) {           // 校验refreshToken有效性及设备指纹           if (!deviceService.validate(refreshToken, currentDeviceId)) {               throw new InvalidTokenException(&quot;无效的Refresh Token&quot;);           }           // 生成新Access Token           return ResponseEntity.ok(jwtService.refreshToken(refreshToken));       }       </code></p>
